      • relativeScaleHint

        public float relativeScaleHint
        Hint indicating relative scaling that is being applied to the scene. The value of this hint indicates the relative number of pixels in the ortho projection that correspond to the number of pixels as displayed in the viewport. To maintain constant pixel size, clients may divide quantities specified in pixels by this value (e.g. line width).
